{"tid":1566502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕節休戰 : 一戰期間的聖誕節中交戰雙方士兵自發的停戰行為","createTime":"2019-09-13T15:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T15:35:00.000Z","uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50a3ec4f24eee626b026ef19cfd8673dd1f55cb2","tid":1566502,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Illustrated_London_News_-_Christmas_Truce_1914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3AIllustrated_London_News_-_Christmas_Truce_1914.jpg&h=c62c2ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕節休戰（英語：Christmas truce）泛指發生於第一次世界大戰期間的平安夜或聖誕節中，德國與英國或是德國與法國軍隊間一些短暫且非官方的休戰，而狹義的聖誕節休戰是指從1914年聖誕節延伸到1915年年初的那段時間，德英軍隊於各自駐紮的西線所發生的休戰行為。此外在1915年德法軍隊之間也有一場聖誕節休戰，而類似的情節也在1916年復活節的東線戰場發生過。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/聖誕節休戰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E7%AF%80%E4%BC%91%E6%88%B0&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88o429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=196431e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/聖誕節休戰</a>"},{"pid":"f87c243429c29f26b1baf9da3e7a0e97ac53ffd0","tid":1566502,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"但香港係被警察狙擊wo"},{"pid":"be1a393ad8b582fb4da33c34ba0134ecf0ddf313","tid":1566502,"uid":278391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"休條撚，紅磡拉左手足啦"},{"pid":"88e5cf06de35fbb1ea065f11d841fbb1df788642","tid":1566502,"uid":47866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"但係香港警察中秋節都唔肯停戰<br />\n佢哋為咗呃人工，到底可以去到幾盡"},{"pid":"b7bac500ab3ea6416a83e5e627137ecdb01ed2f7","tid":1566502,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"中共習帝就是神，聖誕唔識用於支共"},{"pid":"121c76d9f05439ed924dcb2835e694beaba0e660","tid":1566502,"uid":25967